data.description: **OPEN HOUSE, January 21st, 2pm-4pm.**This 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home is located in Brookstone Ridge development includes hardwood style tile floors, natural lighting, neutral colors throughout the house. The gas fireplace gives warmth to the spacious living room. The elegant kitchen features marvelous granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a roomy pantry configured for attractive efficiency. The restful master bedroom includes a walk-in closet and private bath with a large tub, shower, and lots of vanity space.The three additional bedrooms, distributed upstairs for privacy, are rich with ample closet space and ready to reflect your taste in decor. This property also offers a big open bonus room. A driveway with ample accommodation for visiting vehicles leads to an attached three-car garage. Exterior includes jetted hot tub and the right amount of outdoor space. Representing the welcoming personality of the home is a front-facing, breezy front porch. This home is located on a street lined with sidewalks. Solar Panels have already been installed to help reduce energy bills. Great location that is near Kilpatrick Turnpike and I-40. This is a captivating property in the Yukon area. Schedule your showing today!
